OS_Word 21,6
#Parent OS_Word
=>	R0 =	21
	R1 =	pointer to block containing :
		 	0 = 6

<=	block updated :
		 	1 = x	LSB
		 	2 =	MSB
		 	3 = y	LSB
		 	4 =	MSB

This OS_Word reads the pointer position. If the mouse and pointer are linked then the pointer position will be updated with the mouse position each VSync interrupt.
